      "text":"For those of you travelling from Cape Town, you have 2 main options"    
    },
    {
      "name":"Option 1: Road Trip!!",
      "text":"Driving from Cape Town to Rustenburg, it is about a 15 hour drive. It is recommended that you split the drive over 2 days with a sleepover stop in Kimberley. This is a 10 hour drive. From Kimberley, you will be 5 hours away from Rustenburg."    
